Sorry for multiple posts, but I'll put it one final way:<P>Let's say a hard fight lasts 4 minutes, not at all unusual and a purely arbitrary number.<P>If I had an item that gave me clarity at 7 pts a tick, that would be equivalent to 7x10x4 = 280 extra mana to call on, which is the same as having 28 extra wisdom that fight at lvl 50.<P>To take your driving analogy:<P>Take 2 cars, each doing 40 miles to the gallon at 60 mph.<P>Yours can carry 10 gallons.<BR>Mine can only carry 8 gallons, but 'regens' 1 gallon per hour.<P>Yours can drive 400 miles between refills.<BR>Mine, after driving 320 miles (a full tank of 8 gallons worth) still has 5 gallons left.<BR>Mine would travel over twice as far as yours between refills, plus mine would take less time to refill too.<P>The only time mine would suffer is if we both had to drive somewhere at 1000 mph hehe<P>--------------------<P>Elasto, 57 Cleric
